# The furnace has successfully produced 8 iron plates from the iron ore it processed. 

# Now, I will extract the 8 iron plates from the furnace's inventory.

extract_item(Prototype.IronPlate, position=furnace_info.position, quantity=8)  # Extract 8 iron plates from the furnace.
print(f"Inventory changed to {inspect_inventory()}")  # Check the inventory after extraction.
print(f"Entities on the map: {get_entities()}")  # Check the updated state of entities.
